        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownSolitudeFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionHaafingar\")",
        "content": "Sorex Vinius works the floor at the Winking Skeever, his father Corpulus's inn. Loud, friendly Imperial, sweet on Vivienne Onis from the wine cellar.",
