        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownSolitudeFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionHaafingar\")",
        "content": "Jaree-Ra hangs around outside Solitude offering coin to anyone willing to put out the lighthouse. Argonian wrecker, leader of the Blackblood Marauders alongside his sister Deeja — the job is to beach a ship on the rocks.",
