        "content": "Elenwen is the First Emissary of the Thalmor — an Altmer ambassador who runs the Thalmor Embassy in the hills west of Solitude and enforces the Empire's ban on Talos worship with a courteous smile. She hosts lavish parties for Skyrim's nobility; less openly, she ran the interrogation of Ulfric Stormcloak during the Great War, and Ulfric has not forgotten.",
