        "content": "Pelagius Septim III, the Mad — twelfth emperor of the Septim Dynasty — has been dead for centuries, but his fractured mind still inhabits the sealed wing of the Blue Palace that bears his name. Sheogorath keeps his shadow there as a companion. Falk Firebeard would prefer the Pelagius Wing stay shut; the Mad God's priest Dervenin wants someone to go in and bring his master home.",
